OL,6,FJudge Patrick Lynch said the evidence
OL,7,Fpresented against the veteran fell
OL,8,F"well short" of what was required for
OL,9,Fconviction.
OL,11,FThe UK Government confirmed it has
OL,12,Fspent #4.3 million so far, adding the
OL,13,Fsum "may rise marginally" once the
OL,14,Ffinal bills are received.
OL,16,FMinister for Veterans and People
OL,17,FAlistair Cairns revealed the figure
OL,18,Ffollowing a Parliamentary Question
OL,19,F(PQ) asked by SDLP MP for Foyle Colum
OL,20,FEastwood.
