OL,6,FMr Eastwood described it as a "double
OL,7,Finjustice" for the families of those
OL,8,Fkilled during Bloody Sunday
OL,10,F"The government may have left these
OL,11,Fvictims to fight on their own but the
OL,12,Fpeople of Derry never will. We're
OL,13,Fproud of them and we'll keep fighting
OL,14,Ftheir corner," he said in a post on
OL,15,Fsocial media.
OL,17,FSolicitor Ciaran Shiels, of Madden and
OL,18,FFinucane ` who supports some of the
OL,19,FBloody Sunday families, slammed an
OL,20,F"obscene amount of public money".
