OL,6,FIn his response to the PQ, Mr Cairns
OL,7,Fsaid the Ministry of Defence is
OL,8,F"committed to supporting veterans and
OL,9,Ftheir families".
OL,11,FHe said the #4.3 million includes
OL,12,Flegal fees from when Soldier F was
OL,13,Finitially charged in March 2019, and
OL,14,Fcosts associated with a judicial
OL,15,Freview taken against a decision by
OL,16,FNorthern Ireland's Public Prosecution
OL,17,FService (PPS) previously to stop the
OL,18,Fproceedings.
