OL,6,F"As part of this, Soldier F has
OL,7,Freceived legal and welfare support
OL,8,Fthroughout his legal proceedings at
OL,9,Fpublic expense," he said.
OL,11,F"The legal fees associated with these
OL,12,Fproceedings (including associated
OL,13,Fjudicial reviews) amount to #4.3
OL,14,Fmillion, which may rise marginally
OL,15,Fonce final bills are received.
